name: DIMPLES
description: Our FRESH&HUMBLE Tees inspire a trendsetting movement unlike any of todays fashion concepts.  We have created a high performance product with the same capabilities as today's high-tech poly-performance fibers and the feel of organic cotton. The F&H garments are stain, odor, & microbial resistant.  FRESH&HUMBLE Tees are created with three main concepts in mind:  Remain among the Upper Echelon with regards to Quality & Durability, Unparalleled Wicking Technology, and quality that will withstanding the rigors of premium Sublimation and Screen Printing apparatuses. We guarantee this tee will be the lightest, coming in at 5.9oz., and most comfortable tee you’ve ever rocked in you life (made from 100% Premium Combed Ringspun Cotton).  Sizing: S–3XL
